[h3 
	" About the sound plugin
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"MIDAS PSX SPU is better than the TAS Sound Plugin and does not desync. But like the TAS Sound Plugin, it will not play sound during cutscenes and credits.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"NOTE : Sometimes the movie desync at the start of Glimmer. Close and reopen PCSX if this happen, it works fine for me.
	$LF
]p
