[h3 
	" Glitchs
	$LF
]h3
[h4 
	" Dash Jump
	$LF
]h4
[ul 
	[li 
		"What : Make a high jump to reach some inaccessible height.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"How : Press X some frames then press X and square at the same time. Best result are get by only pressing X between 5 and 7 frames.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Where : Everywhere.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h4 
	" Dash Jump Boost
	$LF
]h4
[ul 
	[li 
		"What : Boost a little bit the height of the Dash Jump.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"How : Stop pressing X and square, and only press triangle.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Where : Autumn Plains (skip Climbing) and Winter Tundra.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h4 
	" Swim in the air
	$LF
]h4
[ul 
	[li 
		"What : Read tittle.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"How : After having learnt to swim, dash or headbash in water when you are OOB. You will swim, but since you are OOB, the game will never stop your swim animation until you change level or reach a water surface.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Where : Winter Tundra
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h4 
	" Camera glitch
	$LF
]h4
[ul 
	[li 
		"What : Like in many 3D games, some events happen or not happen depending of the camera orientation.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"How : L2 or R2 (don't work during a dash attack).
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Where : Zephyr
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 
	" Comments
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"To finish the game, you need to beat Ripto. Thanks to the swim in the air glitch, that means you need to go to Winter Tundra i.e. beat Gulp. No one have never find a way to fight Gulp without the 14 talismans, so you need them to finish the game.
	$LF
]p
