	" Ripto
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"All upgrades makes 10 damages at the first hit, then 4 for all others. Ripto have 60 hp and "Meca Gulp" have 80 hp. With some timing, you can kill Meca Gulp with only 3 upgrades (since green upgrade can make 30 damages to him).
	$LF
